        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Quick Start Guide",
        "text": "<h2>Quick Start Guide</h2><p>[wistia_video]</p><p>Ready to begin? To get started with your first treatment, you’ll need the following:</p><ul><li>Q-Renew LLLT Helmet</li><li>Charging Base (provided)</li><li>USB-C Charging Cable (provided)</li></ul>"
      }
    },
