      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content-image-block.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Charging Your Device",
        "text": "<h2>Charging Your Device</h2><p>[image]</p><p>Connect the included USB-C cable to the charging base and plug it into a 5V power adapter (not included).</p><p>Tap the LCD screen to check charging progress.</p><p>Full charge time is approximately 4 hours.</p><ul><li>The device will not operate while charging.</li><li>Ensure all ports are completely dry before charging.</li></ul><p>Tips to maximize battery life:</p><ul><li>Avoid leaving your device charging for long periods of time.</li><li>Avoid letting the battery completely run out.</li><li>Do not use your device while it’s connected to the charger.</li></ul>"
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_EgcRqf": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Care & Storage",
        "text": "<h2>Care & Storage</h2><h6>Cleaning</h6><ul><li>Wipe with a damp cloth or water-based wipe.</li><li>For stubborn spots, gently use 70% alcohol.</li><li>Optionally, spray the inside with Qure Dermal Mist before wiping to help maintain freshness.</li><li>Do not clean while the device is on or charging.</li><li>Avoid abrasive materials, solvents, or cleaners.</li></ul><p>[hr]</p><h6>Storage</h6><ul><li>Allow the device to cool completely before storing.</li><li>Keep in a dry, room-temperature location, away from sunlight or humidity.</li><li>Use the charging base or original box for safe storage.</li><li>Do not expose to extreme temperatures or physical damage.</li></ul>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_DDFqeM": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Troubleshooting & Adjustments",
        "text": "<h2>Troubleshooting & Adjustments</h2><p>Having trouble? Don’t worry, most issues are quick to solve.</p><h6>Device is not turning on</h6><ul><li>Ensure the charging cable is securely connected to the power outlet.</li><li>Ensure the charging cable is securely connected to the device and charge it fully.</li><li>Try a different power outlet.</li><li>Press and hold the on/off button for at least one second.</li></ul><p>[hr]</p><h6>Device is turning off too early</h6><p>The battery level may be too low — charge the product fully and try again.</p><p>[hr]</p><h6>Something else?</h6><p>DO NOT attempt to investigate or modify the product. It contains no serviceable parts.</p><p>If the issue persists, please contact Qure Support at <a href=\"mailto:support@qureskincare.com\">support@qureskincare.com</a> for further assistance.</p>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
